message.body: Hey man, where can a brother get some banging wings in Philly?
Where in Philly are you living right now? I'll see if i can recommend somewhere good
I'm in the art museum area, but looking for a place down town
I've been told Moriarty's is supposed to have good wings. Haven't had them yet. Just a warning though, it's an Irish bar so it's prob real bro'ed out there
Haha anytime man! I'm going to be a on feature in DE until around the holidays, but we should hang when I get back
Bet. I knew I can always count on you haha.
Yeah man! That's awesome. I'm working for NFL till february so I'll be around.
